Novation to Sell Corvisa to ShoreTel

December 21, 2015 - Novation Companies, Inc. (OTCQB: NOVC) (“Novation”) today announced that it is selling Corvisa LLC to ShoreTel, Inc. (NASDAQ: SHOR)...View full story.

Corvisa Goes Global with Network Presence in London and Amsterdam

November 17, 2015 - Cloud communications provider, Corvisa LLC, announced today that it will bring its unique combination of PaaS and SaaS solutions to the global market...View full story.

Novation Companies Announces Changes of Executive Team

August 17, 2015 - Novation Companies, Inc. (OTCQB: NOVC) (“Novation”) today announced that W. Lance Anderson delivered notice of his resignation to the Board of Directors, effective Friday, Aug. 14, 2015, retiring after nearly 20 years with the company...View full story.

Corvisa Announces Three Executive Appointments

June 18, 2015 - Company strengthens leadership team by adding industry veterans from inContact, Workfront and Empower Software Solutions
...View full story.

Corvisa Named 2015 Hot Vendor

May 29, 2015 - Corvisa LLC, a provider of cloud communications solutions, has been selected as a 2015 Hot Vendor in Real-Time Communication and Collaboration Platform as a Service by Aragon Research, a leading technology research and advisory firm...View full story.

Novation Announces Agreement with Lone Star Value

April 22, 2015 - Novation Companies, Inc. ("Novation" or the "Company") today announced that it has entered into an agreement with Lone Star Value Management, LLC and its affiliates ("Lone Star Value").  Novation has agreed to expand the size of the Company's Board of Directors...View full story.

Corvisa Announces Partnership with Intelisys

April 21, 2015 - Cloud communications provider, Corvisa LLC, today announced a strategic partnership with Intelisys, the country’s largest technology services distributor...View full story.

Corvisa Acquires Codebox to Enhance Open Source Tools for Developers

